DISCLAIMER: 

All Assets in this project were imported from the "Unreal Engine 
C++ Developer: Learn C++ and Make Video Games" course created by GameDev.tv (website, 
as of date, located at https://www.gamedev.tv/). If you want to reuse them for your 
purposes, please check with the original creators to make sure for compliance.

Modular SciFi Season 1 Starter Bundle is available for free at the Marketplace of
Epic Games Launcher (check https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/modular-scifi-season-1-starter-bundle).
If you want to reuse these assets for your purposes please check with the original 
creator to make sure for compliance.

Paragon: Wraith is available for free at the Marketplace of Epic Games Launcher
(check https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/paragon-wraith).
If you want to reuse these assets for your purposes please check with the original 
creator to make sure for compliance.

The Headshot sound effect was imported from soundboard.com(
(check https://www.soundboard.com/sb/sound/934539 ). The asset is marked for
personal use (which excludes commercial uses). If you want to reuse this asset for your purposes, 
please check with the original creator to make sure for compliance.

The pull trigger (on empty cartridge) sound effect was imported from freesound.org
(check https://freesound.org/people/Nanashi/sounds/104412/ ). This asset is under
the CC0 1.0 Universal (CC0 1.0) license. If you want to reuse this asset for your purposes, 
please check with the original creator to make sure for compliance.

